<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>新鲜的十二个有趣的笑话。来自俄罗斯的笑话。</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/</link><description>来自俄罗斯的轶事是最有趣的笑话，故事，格言和短语，诗歌，漫画和其他幽默。他们于1995年11月8日发布。由Dima Werner编译</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>轶事＃1 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510860</link><description>克里姆林宫说，他准备成为美国和乌克兰之间和平谈判中的中介。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510860</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃2 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510861</link><description>泽伦斯基（Zelensky）在历史上倒下了 - 所以自莫妮卡·莱文斯基（Monica Levinsky）时代以来，在白宫就没有人！</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510861</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃3 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510862</link><description>教父2.0&lt;br /&gt;特朗普 -  Zelensky：&lt;br /&gt; - 是的，您要达成协议，但我想在不u-wing的情况下做到这一点！</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510862</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃4 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510863</link><description>- 你应该离开...&lt;br /&gt; - 从办公室？&lt;br /&gt; - 更远...&lt;br /&gt; - 来自白宫？&lt;br /&gt; - 更远...&lt;br /&gt; - 来自美国的家？&lt;br /&gt; - 更远...&lt;br /&gt; - 从总统的职位？&lt;br /&gt; - 更远！</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510863</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃5 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510864</link><description>那个女孩以灰烬来找她的朋友：&lt;br /&gt; - 哦，你有煎饼，有什么？&lt;br /&gt; - 有罪的感觉</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510864</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃6 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510865</link><description>您能想象如果他们喝了橙汁会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510865</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃7 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510866</link><description>- 总统先生，您应该知道...&lt;br /&gt; - 可以留下...&lt;br /&gt; - 也许首先从白宫失败，然后...</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510866</guid></item><item><title>02 Martha 2025的轶事＃8</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510867</link><description>- 今天，我整夜都有一个鲁ck的仇恨！&lt;br /&gt; - 哇！那是谁？&lt;br /&gt; - 左右！</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510867</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃9 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510868</link><description>谁是最大的计划，最常见的是人类的去向？&lt;br /&gt; - 医生监管学家。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510868</guid></item><item><title>anecdot＃10 for 02 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510869</link><description>金发 - 妇科医生：&lt;br /&gt; - 医生，告诉我，您认为最可靠的避孕手段是什么？&lt;br /&gt; - 蜡烛！&lt;br /&gt; ...&lt;br /&gt;一段时间后，再次来：&lt;br /&gt; - 医生，您需要解雇此类建议！我对整个卧室厌倦了蜡烛，仍然飞过！</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-02/#1510869</guid></item></channel></rss>